- friendsofphp/php-cs-fixer: 3.87.2 → 3.88.2
- peter-evans/dockerhub-description: 4 → 5
- phpunit/phpunit: 12.3.14 → 12.3.15
- postgres: 17-alpine → 18-alpine in /doc/deploy
